织，并在加沙地带建立一个新的「安全政权」。 加兰特表示，战争将分为三个主要阶段：第一阶段通过空袭开展军事行动，后进行地面行动，目标是消灭武装力量和破坏基础设施，从而击败和摧毁哈马斯；第二阶段将继续强度较低的战斗，以部队将「消除零星抵抗」；第三阶段将在加沙地带建立新的安全制度，为以色列人民和当地人创造安全环境。（总台记者 江浩宇）更多资讯请下载央视新闻客户端"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-7b98b63cabee7e9564a15f7906c0c8f0_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "93 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/627055903"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIyM6h0aiB8ftZEAMaCTEwMTYyNDYzNiDb28mpBjAAOKoGQAZyCTYyNzA1NTkwM3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1697821349.945622", "card_id": "Q_627018475", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 32}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价《乐队的夏天》第三季第十一期？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "93 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/627018475"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IyM6h0aiB8ftZEAMaCTEwMTYxNjM2MyChj8mpBjAAOCNAB3IJNjI3MDE4NDc1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1697821349.945935", "card_id": "Q_626974401", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 18}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价《披荆斩棘》第三季第九期？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "74 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/626974401"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IyM6h0aiB8ftZE