座小镇上刺死一名 6 岁男孩并刺伤男孩母亲。当地警方称，此次袭击事件与受害者宗教信仰和当前巴以冲突有关系。这引发美国各界对仇恨犯罪的担忧。 比利时首都布鲁塞尔 16 日晚发生枪击事件，造成两名瑞典球迷死亡，另有一人受伤。比利时国家危机中心随后宣布，布鲁塞尔大区的安全警戒级别提升至最高级 4 级。一名自称凶手的人在社交媒体上宣称，自己效忠极端组织「伊斯兰国」。 18 日至 19 日，美国在中东地区多个军事基地连续遭袭。美军中央司令部已证实，美军在伊拉克的基地遭袭并造成军人受伤。突发！多国爆发致命袭击，美军多个基地遭袭！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-16245a3c1c61eafa09223e9c83a550f8_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "40 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/626983350"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIyM6h0aiB8ftZEAMaCTEwMTYwODYyMSCagcipBjAAOPkFQBRyCTYyNjk4MzM1MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1697821349.952425", "card_id": "Q_626916502", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 301}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些机圈人奉行的购机「省学指南」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "每到双 11，最热闹的还是数码类，本小白面对双 11 琳琅满目的选购技巧前，想问问机圈人有哪些「数码省学指南」能抄作业？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "40 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/626916502"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIyM6h0aiB8ftZEAMaCTEwMTU5Mzg5MiDigMWpBjAAON4CQBVyCTYyNjkxNjUwMngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1697821349.952772", "card_id": "Q_455513991", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 55}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "中国机床在国际上大概的地位是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "中国机床在国际上大概的地位是什么？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-8d330e464b2a059db9ef4c2560b21789_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "40 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/455513991"